caption: Very slow making tacos while she talks about her mundane relationship life to her coworker who wasn't listening.. She was basically talking to herself. You got good things there but the people are make it low standard. I'll pass on this location forever.

This is NOT a 7-Eleven. It is a Stripes. I drove a long ways to get to this place and I was very disappointed. They do have a Slurpee machine that has some drinks that you usually find it in 7-Eleven but again, it is NOT a 7-Eleven!
Great gas station. Very clean and great prices on drinks.
